{"tid":2152762,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《花木蘭》會在中國上映 「不朽傳奇 全新演繹 即將綻放影院」","createTime":"2020-08-12T07:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T03:01:02.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dd429c2e9744eea453878462375f6f0d5d6c1935","tid":2152762,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:18:46.000Z","msg":"迪士尼今天公布，《花木蘭》（MULAN）會在中國國內戲院上上映。微博上已經證實該電影獲准在中國上映，在中國版的海報上寫道：「不朽傳奇 全新演繹」，在片名下方則寫著：「即將綻放影院」。<br />\n<br />\n目前尚未確認上映日期。這部電影將於9月4日在Disney+上映，到時候有Disney+這項服務的國家可以在其平台上購買收看。而在其他國家是會在電影院上映，由於迪士尼在中國「深根」已久而且有兩位主要角色非常「愛國」，所以迪士尼相當寄望於中國市場的成功。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/geekbase/159714723590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fgeekbase%2F159714723590.jpg&h=d4d88a43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8dbef24d2f39e6f4f37e452326b5fdee8459a669","tid":2152762,"uid":171849,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:30:22.000Z","msg":"堂堂disney大片個poster整到咁既樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a11eb8361572a9f3aa6777cb830637ef350bc29","tid":2152762,"uid":25525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:32:17.000Z","msg":"又十九幾億票房"},{"pid":"0a286d9d56e6412af9a4405029381d0d07c3e39d","tid":2152762,"uid":32464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:33:17.000Z","msg":"個style好八十年代剪貼出黎咁"},{"pid":"74d554a5e0565faf08c8b2e49416b4383d388d63","tid":2152762,"uid":294953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:34:34.000Z","msg":"住係美國<br />\n愛邊個國先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cee1adf1a7b1d3bd123703fd26ac22db80c22cb","tid":2152762,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:37:33.000Z","msg":"劉亦菲呢個洋奴漢奸走狗賣国賊<br />\n有中国人唔做 走去做美國人既狗<br />\n身為愛国既中国人都應該要罷睇呢套戲！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class